        bindings = <

                &kp TAB             &mt LG(N7) N7   &mt LG(N8) N8   &mt LG(N9) N9   &mt LG(N0) N0          &none    &none       &none       &none       &none
                &mt LCTRL BSPC      &mt LG(N4) N4   &mt LG(N5) N5   &mt LG(N6) N6   &mt SPACE MINUS        &none    &kp LSHFT   &kp LGUI    &kp LALT    &kp LCTRL
    &trans      &mt LS(RET) RET     &mt LG(N1) N1   &mt LG(N2) N2   &mt LG(N3) N3   &mt LS(SEMI) DOT       &none    &none       &trans      &trans      &trans        &trans
